            <title>[LUDOC-457] readcache max file size moved in 2.12.x and newer</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-457</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As described in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12768&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12768&lt;/a&gt;,&#160;the&#160;readcache_max_filesize tunable has moved from obdfilter to osd-{ldiskfs,zfs}.&#160; The manual must be updated to reflect this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
