                            <comment id="254999" author="simmonsja" created="Wed, 18 Sep 2019 17:04:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just got my test bed back and tried this out.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lctl list_param *.&lt;b&gt;OST000&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;b&gt;readcache&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obdfilter.lustre-OST0000.readcache_max_filesize&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;obdfilter.lustre-OST0002.readcache_max_filesize&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;osd-ldiskfs.lustre-OST0000.readcache_max_filesize&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;osd-ldiskfs.lustre-OST0002.readcache_max_filesize&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now if you try obdfilter version it gives a warning not to use it anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
